WEBVTT

00:06:58.720 --> 00:07:01.640
we are a carbon neutral country.

00:07:03.480 --> 00:07:05.240
Turns out, it's a big deal.

00:07:05.920 --> 00:07:08.296
Of the 200-odd countries
in the world today,

00:07:08.320 --> 00:07:10.080
it looks like we are the only one

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:11.800
that's carbon neutral.

00:07:13.520 --> 00:07:15.480
Actually, that's not quite accurate.

00:07:17.040 --> 00:07:18.880
Bhutan is not carbon neutral.

00:07:19.920 --> 00:07:22.240
Bhutan is carbon negative.

00:07:23.600 --> 00:07:30.536
Our entire country generates
2.2 million tons of carbon dioxide,